The napkin was the exact size and color as the original, and both the sketch
and the signature looked authentic...it was the Empi logo that gave it away
as a repro.  VOA lawyers have contacted Empi about the unauthorized
reproduction and the use of the name "Ben" which VOA has trademarked.

